##### MF3: REACTION CROSS SECTIONS                                3428 1451
                                                                  3428 1451
All the data present in the following MT-sections have been       3428 1451
calculated with TALYS, possibly normalized to experimental data.  3428 1451
If the maximal cross section in an excitation function over the   3428 1451
whole energy range does not exceed 1.e-9 b, the MT-number is not  3428 1451
included. Cross sections lower than 1.e-20 b are assumed to have  3428 1451
no physical meaning and are set to zero. All MT numbers extend up 3428 1451
to the highest incident energy.                                   3428 1451
The following reaction channels/MT numbers are generally included:3428 1451
                                                                  3428 1451
- MT1      : Total cross section                                  3428 1451
                                                                  3428 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range,    3428 1451
or partly reproduced using experimental data.                     3428 1451
                                                                  3428 1451
- MT2      : Elastic scattering cross section                     3428 1451
                                                                  3428 1451
Obtained by subtracting the non-elastic cross section from the    3428 1451
total cross section.                                              3428 1451
                                                                  3428 1451
- MT3      : Non-elastic cross section                            3428 1451
                                                                  3428 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range.    3428 1451
                                                                  3428 1451
- MT4      : Total inelastic cross section                        3428 1451
                                                                  3428 1451
Sum of MT=51-91.                                                  3428 1451
                                                                  3428 1451
- MT5      : (n,anything) cross section                           3428 1451
                                                                  3428 1451
MT5 contains the reactions which can not be stored in any other   3428 1451
